    <briefdescription>
<para>One fully parsed sample from the ADS1299. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>channels[] contain sign-extended 24-bit values in LSB units.</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Convert to microvolts: uV = channels[n] * (VREF / gain / 8388607.0)</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>where VREF = 4.5V for ADS1299, and gain is set per channel in CHnSET. </para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
    </detaileddescription>
